data.description: Welcome to 7 Fiddleleaf in Panther Creek subdivision in The Woodlands.  Completely remodeled down to the studs after frozen pipe in February freeze 2021.  Luxurious architect designed home with new pex piping, new roof 6/22, hardy plank exterior, new wiring and electrical, with blown insulation in the walls and attic.  Open designer kitchen, stainless steel appliances, Quartz countertops, gas range with hood vent, farm sink, soft close drawers, LED lighting, and large double paned windows.  Luxurious primary suite with an office or second living space, oversized walkin closet, jetted tub, seamless shower with river stone flooring. Make your appointment or schedule a private tour today.
